00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:49.000
"What is this 16-year-old boy doing with these 12-year-old boys?"

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:51.000
And he did spend a lot of time up to no good.

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.000
