00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.000
He looks out his window; he calls me upstairs; he said, "Hey Anthony."

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:26.000
They called me Anthony growing up as a kid.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:28.000
